Package: RSymHOMALS
Type: Package
Title: Symbolic HOMALS for Multi-Valued Categorical Data
Version: 0.2.1
Authors@R: c(person("Han-Ming", "Wu", email = "wuhm@g.nccu.edu.tw", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Chiun-How", "Kao", role = "aut"))
Author: Han-Ming Wu [aut, cre],
  Chiun-How Kao [aut]
Maintainer: Han-Ming Wu <wuhm@g.nccu.edu.tw>
Description: Tools for fitting Symbolic HOMALS models to multi-valued
    categorical data, comparing Euclidean, Hausdorff, Wasserstein, and
    naive multiple correspondence analysis baselines, and rebuilding the
    simulation, diagnostic, benchmark, and empirical analyses used in the
    accompanying manuscript.
